snippet.title: Mixed Super Mario Bros. U - Trailer 2
snippet.description:
NOTE: Mixed Super Mario Bros. U is no longer in development and is now cancelled!

Mixed SMBU was a mod created by a team of people for NSMBU that was originally meant to be released in 2021 but later got pushed back to 2022. As of October 2021; the mod is officially cancelled and is no longer in development, meaning it will not be released.

The trailer was recorded and edited by @Rimea, the trailer theme was created by @goatsoup which is also part of the mod's soundtrack!

This trailer was also shown in the New Super Mario Bros. U Modding Direct by Rimea: https://youtu.be/u2-FXKWj1Cs
